# Sealed Secrets are encrypted with the cluster's controller key and
# safe to commit. Whitelist only the encrypted YAMLs + README so any
# accidental plaintext file in the same directory still stays ignored.
!hetzner/myapp/monitoring/secrets/
hetzner/myapp/monitoring/secrets/*
!hetzner/myapp/monitoring/secrets/*.sealedsecret.yaml
!hetzner/myapp/monitoring/secrets/README.md

